M|references|Comprehensive list of events to track by business type and ctx.
M|references|- mkt Site Events (navigation & engagement, CTA & form interactions, conversion events)
M|references|- Product/App Events (onboarding, core usage, errors & support)
M|references|- Monetization Events (pricing & checkout, subscription management)
M|references|- E-commerce Events (browsing, cart, checkout, post-purchase)
M|references|- B2B / SaaS Specific Events (team & collaboration, integration events, account events)
M|references|- Event Properties (Parameters)
M|references|- Funnel Event Sequences
